These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | biathlon | weightlifting | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, pomegranate, broccoli
1. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating peas is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | peas | broccoli | pomegranate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, singing, writing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | traveling | singing | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, indie, soul
1. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | soul | indie |

